{"id":"ecfa4111-6225-4016-8c26-38c2fb756359","name":"Fate/Grand Order 𝐑𝐏𝐆","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>\"Good morning, Senpai.\"</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/yL4P7xs888wrzlXAeoFnC.gif\" alt=\"Banner.gif\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\"><em>The </em></span><strong><em>Organization for the Preservation of Human Order, Finis Chaldea </em></strong><em>or simply</em><strong><em>, \"Chaldea\"</em></strong><em>, </em><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\"><em>a secret agency founded with the purpose of preventing the \"certain extinction\" of the human race. It was founded by Marisbury Animusphere,</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\"><em>Chaldea specializes in handling temporal anomalies and other existential threats to humanity, with the help of their Masters, and their Servants in order to restore the foundation of those singularities.</em></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\">‎</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/nLGH1mTJkvhanReG8_wLj.webp\" alt=\"Fate System.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Using the </em><strong><em>Guardian Heroic Spirit Summoning System \"FATE\"</em></strong><em>, </em><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\"><em>Chaldeans who are considered \"provisional Masters\" are able to summon Heroic Spirits as Servants. This system was made after the Fuyuki Holy Grail System, accessing the </em><strong><em>Throne of Heroes</em></strong><em>, thus, allowing a contract of Master and Servant.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(230, 230, 230);\"><em>There are currently 15 registered classes. Some of which are beyond the Standard 7, and some who are 